  "title": "ISic003348. Tyndaris honours Antimachos as Euergetes",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy 2022-07-12 Prag, in the Antiquarium</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ὁ δᾶμος <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀντίμαχον\n                    Φίλωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀντίμαχον\">Ἀντίμαχον</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φίλωνος\">Φίλωνος</span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[ε]ὐεργέταν </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy 2022-07-12 Prag, in the Antiquarium</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΟΔΑΜΟΣ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀντίμαχον\n                    Φίλωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀντίμαχον\">ΑΝΤΙΜΑΧΟΝ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φίλωνος\">ΦΙΛΩΝΟΣ</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[.]ΥΕΡΓΕΤΑΝ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003348_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022/07/14\" src=\"ISic003348_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003348.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022/07/14\" src=\"ISic003348-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003348_left_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022/07/14\" src=\"ISic003348_left_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003348_left.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022/07/14\" src=\"ISic003348_left-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003348_right_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022/07/14\" src=\"ISic003348_right_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003348_right.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022/07/14\" src=\"ISic003348_right-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003348_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022/07/14\" src=\"ISic003348_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003348.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022/07/14\" src=\"ISic003348-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text from autopsy</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Gentili:[Ἀρισ]τόδαμος... </span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>The people (honours) Antimachos son of Philo, benefactor</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1953.0277 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a></li><li> Gentili 1952 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001959\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001959</a></li><li> Manganaro 1965 203 no.2 tav.72.4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841</a></li><li> Fasolo 2013 58 no.3 fig.21 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002011\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002011</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Simply cut, regular letters of fairly wide module, without serifs. Alpha with broken bar; epsilon with shorter middle stroke; Mu with full length strokes, vertical first and last; omicron almost full size; sigma with horizontal outer strokes, inner strokes almost full width; phi with extended vertical (up to 65mm), small circular eye; omega closed, with tear-drop shape. </p> Line 1  36-42  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
